show.description: Driven by envy and a relentless need to outshine Christina, Reena schemed to shatter her world. But in the chaos she created, Christina crossed paths with Alex—an encounter that lasted just one unforgettable night. Five years later, destiny intervenes, and their lives collide once more. What fueled Reena’s deep-rooted jealousy? And how did that single night alter the course of Christina and Alex’s lives forever?
